<definition>[Equated Results]
Let <m>A</m> be a zero sum matrix game. A strategy <m>\textbf{p}</m> for Rose <term>equates Colin's Results</term> if all entries of <m>\textbf{p}A</m> are equal. Likewise, a strategy <m>\textbf{q}</m> for Colin \textbf{equates Rose's Results} if all entries of <m>A\textbf{q}</m> are equal.
</definition>

